  "user_id": 14639,
  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Hammer Time\r\n\r\nThis remix of Hammer Time mixes in jazz, funk, and hip-hop elements using bold beats and smooth instrument layers. Listen for repeated brass, bass, and piano parts. Each section is organized into functions like Lead, piano, and Break it down so the student could build and experiment with different sounds more easily. There is a clear intro and outro.\r\n \r\n**Note from the creator:**\r\n> For this remix, I wanted to blend the original track with a jazzy, kind of chaotic vibe. I made different functions for each part of the song so I could focus on building layers without cluttering the code. I used one function just to handle all the wild sounds, `chaos` and brought it in with repeats to make it feel unpredictable. It was fun figuring out how to combine brass hits and piano loops to keep the beat fresh but still familiar.",
    "offer_browser_tts": "true",
    "use_secondary_finish_button": "false",
    "hide_share_and_remix": "true",
    "predict_settings": {
      "isPredictLevel": false
    },
